title: [Seethe Naedal, Crags]
description: The path continues upward through a channel in the rock before changing to crudely carved steps that provide a precarious way up through the rocky terrain.  A family of birds have built a nest not far off the path.

The path continues upward through a channel in the rock before changing to crudely carved steps that provide a precarious way up through the rocky terrain towards the stars.  A family of birds have built a nest not far off the path.
